Retro - A widescreen theme for MythTV

The old Retro theme based on the excellent Blue-abstract theme from Robert Siebert.


COMPATIBILITY
=============

* Works for MythTV 0.24 & 0.25 (not all new screens are supported)

INSTALL
=======

* got into directory of your choice
* clone the repo: git clone git://github.com/notz/Retro-wide.git 
* link the theme: sudo ln -s Retro-wide /usr/share/mythtv/themes/

